casebody.data:
ALLSTATE INSURANCE COMPANY, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
AUTO CLUB INSURANCE ASSOCIATION, Defendant-Appellant. Allstate Insurance Company, Plaintiff,
v.
Marquise Dionne Harris, Defendant. SC: 156773
COA: 338895 Supreme Court of Michigan. September 12, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's July 3, 2018 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because it does not appear that the order was entered erroneously.
